HEADWORD: Mithraism
<hw>Mithraism</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The ancient Persian religion
which worshiped <persfn>Mithra</persfn>; it was popular among Romans
during first three centuries <sc>a. d.</sc></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Mithraicism.</syn>⟦br⟧
